Author: MuddyWalruss
Text: This one friend i have loooooves to talk about food and weight loss and i get so uncomfortable especially because she knows about my ED problems. It's like she directs them at me.

Author: slushypandaboobs
Text: Ugh yesssss! Someone always has to bring up their latest diets but I think it’s because the food culture is really pushing paleo, keto, veganism, and intermittent fasting. It’s just so boring and whenever someone talks about carbs being the devil, I just want to jump off a cliff because they’re my safe food
